summary: Hate the ugly, broken down, dead appearance and feeling of the exterior of Skyhaven Temple? Then this is the mod for you, replacing the dead trees with beautiful Aspen trees, the overgrown shrubs with colourful flowers and bushes and adding a more lively appearance with npcs and more.
descriptionHtml:
Hate the ugly, broken down, dead appearance and feeling of the exterior of Skyhaven Temple? Then this is the mod for you, replacing the dead trees with beautiful Aspen trees, the overgrown shrubs with colorful flowers and bushes and adding a more lively appearance with new npc's, free storage, equipment to use and more.

This is my first mod and I'm going to update the mod until I feel it is fully complete. Any suggestions please message me or type it below in the comment section. Report any bugs to me or issues that disrupt gameplay. Feel free to suggest it to friends. If you wish you may create a video or post pictures online of my mod.

Please any constructive criticism will be very useful anything you want added or changed suggest your ideas and opinions. I'm very open-minded.

REQUIRES:
LATEST UPDATE OF SKYRIM.

[size=3][b]YOU NEED TO HAVE REACHED THE ALDUINS WALL QUESTLINE TO ACCESS SKYHAVEN TEMPLE. THE FAST TRAVEL TO SKYHAVEN TEMPLE IS NOT USEABLE WITHOUT BEING UP TO THE BLADES QUESTLINE IT WILL ONLY GET YOU PUSHED OFF THE HILL BECAUSE THERE IS A BORDER![/b][/size]
author: jj123thefunky
